longBusinessSummary: GRN Holding Corporation does not have significant operations. The company intends to merge with another entity. Previously, it was involved in the gold exploration and development activities. The company was formerly known as Discovery Gold Corporation and changed its name to GRN Holding Corporation in September 2019. GRN Holding Corporation was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Seattle, Washington.
